<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
   <head>
      <title>Bull Rush</title>
      <link href="/stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
      <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
   </head>
   <body>
      <h2>Bull Rush</h2>
      <div class="container-fluid" id="canvas_container"></div>
      <div class="row">
         <div class="col-sm-4">
            <h1>Score: 0</h2>
         </div>
         <div class="col-sm-4">
            <button onClick="addHighscore()">End Game</button>
         </div>
         <div class="col-sm-4">
			<input id="seed" type="number" value="" placeholder="Random Seed">
		 </div>
      </div>
      <table>
         <tr>
            <td>
               <div/>
            </td>
            <td>
               <div class="dpad" onClick="dpadInput('PadUp')"></div>
            </td>
            <td>
               <div/>
            </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
            <td>
               <div class="dpad" onClick="dpadInput('PadLeft')"></div>
            </td>
            <td>
               <div class="dpad" onClick="dpadInput('PadWait')"></div>
            </td>
            <td>
               <div class="dpad" onClick="dpadInput('PadRight')"></div>
            </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
            <td>
               <div/>
            </td>
            <td>
               <div class="dpad" onClick="dpadInput('PadDown')"></div>
            </td>
            <td>
               <div/>
            </td>
         </tr>
      </table>
      <div class="row">
         <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2>Instructions</h2>
            <div class="instructions">
               <p>Youâ€™re the blue square</p>
               <p>White squares are your friends</p>
               <p>Red Squares are not your friends</p>
               <p>Arrow keys/WASD to move, Space to wait</p>
               <p>Hold ctrl or alt to stun a creature in a given direction<br> or if it's a red square just walk into it and hope for the best.</p>
               <p><a href="itsmaze.herokuapp.com">Also check out Max's Maze Game</a></p>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2>High Scores</h2>
            <div>
               <table>
                  <% for(var i=0; i<scores.length; i++) { %>
                  <tr>
                     <td class="score_col">
                        <%= scores[i].name %>
                     </td>
                     <td class="score_col">
                        <%= scores[i].score %>
                     </td>
                  </tr>
                  <% } %>
               </table>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="../javascripts/bullrush.js"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="../javascripts/astar.js"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="../javascripts/prng.js"></script>
   </body>
</html>